data.description:
Welcome to Deer Creek at its finest! This exquisite home is nestled on a beautiful cul-de-sac street, offering a prime location within the coveted Carillion Pod. Boasting three bedrooms and two full baths, this residence spans over 2100 square feet of living space.

The backyard is an absolute delight, featuring a fully fenced yard with a firepit near the covered patio, perfect for cozy evenings and outdoor gatherings.  The well-thought-out floor plan includes a formal living room, a dining room, a family room perfect for entertaining, and a kitchen with a convenient breakfast bar and a nook with built in seating in a bay window.

Indulge in the luxury of the master suite, complete with a spacious walk-in closet and a master bath that includes a jetted tub and a separate shower. This home combines comfort, style, and functionality, creating a perfect haven for you and your family.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your new home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the charm and elegance of Deer Creek living!
